场景重现： 
cd 那个目录的时候 出现如下错误 You are using '.rvmrc', it requires trusting, it is slower and it is not compatible with other ruby managers,
you can switch to '.ruby-version' using 'rvm rvmrc to [.]ruby-version'
or ignore this warnings with 'rvm rvmrc warning ignore /home/andy/Documents/tianjicom/.rvmrc',
'.rvmrc' will continue to be the default project file in RVM 1 and RVM 2,
to ignore the warning for all files run 'rvm rvmrc warning ignore all.rvmrcs'.

lUsing /home/andy/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.3-p448 with gemset rails3.2.12

解决方法:

rvm rvmrc warning ignore /home/andy/Documents/tianjicom/.rvmrc

